msgid ""
"Moves created through this stock request will be put in this procurement "
"group. If none is given, the moves generated by procurement rules will be "
"grouped into one big picking."
msgstr ""
"Os movementos creados a través desta solicitude de existencias colocaranse "
"neste grupo de compras. Se non se proporciona ningún, os movementos xerados "
"polas regras de adquisición agruparanse nunha gran selección."

